# =============================================================================
# SECURITY BEST PRACTICES
# =============================================================================
#
# 1. Key Rotation:
#    - Rotate API keys quarterly
#    - Update in Vercel immediately after rotation
#    - Test thoroughly after updates
#
# 2. Key Separation:
#    - Use different keys for production vs preview/dev
#    - Never use production keys in development
#    - Never use test keys in production
#
# 3. Access Control:
#    - Limit Vercel project access to necessary team members
#    - Use Vercel Teams for enterprise deployments
#    - Enable 2FA on all service accounts
#
# 4. Monitoring:
#    - Set up billing alerts for all paid APIs
#    - Monitor API usage dashboards
#    - Set rate limits where available
#
# 5. Secret Management:
#    - Never commit secrets to git
#    - Use .gitignore for .env files
#    - Review git history before pushing
#
# =============================================================================

